kawa
---

the package manager for the chiyoko linux distribution


REQUIRED FILES:
- /etc/kawa.d/repos.conf, example:
```example
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chiyokolinux/packages/main/packages.db
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chiyokolinux/packages/community/packages.db
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chiyokolinux/packages/contrib/packages.db
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chiyokolinux/packages/nonfree/packages.db
```
- more to come? i don't know
